    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know, i should call them but it's the weekend and the clinic is closed. i really need something now. i've taken ibuprofen many times before and it always works for my headaches, it's just a little bit. is it really thats dangerous to just take one or two pills to get through the night?",
